Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢冈崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你为难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然听到我这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但憋在心里实在太难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们俩才刚认识不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说常和杏三人一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我不是说讨厌你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是没把你当做恋爱的对象看待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这样说太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就试着交往看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今后还要慢慢地互相加深了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 这段过程不是作为普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而试着以恋人的身份来度过也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起你就是我的女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪…止不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDCFCD2&\3c&H89B87E&\4c&H6F9149&\shad1\bord1\pos(432,320)\fad(450,0)}另一个世界 杏篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你打算去学护理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是我从小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还都没怎么考虑过将来的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我觉得不用着急的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么无所事事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你都会嫌弃我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都不会嫌弃冈崎同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前都没有人和我说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有点感激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～ 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的星期天你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好陪着椋怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 用不着你操心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从高二开始就喜欢你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你感觉能顺利交往下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不但认真 而且温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说她动不动就会脸红这点要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是她的可爱之处呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 你还真疼妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和椋接吻过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！哪…哪有啊 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 你要更主动一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子交往 我这还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要练习一下试试吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当做是椋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是双胞胎 气质也很像对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是练习嘛 真的亲到了怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 难道你当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是那样 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还算是及格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在那个公园里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎是指那个不良少年吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他们两个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们以前是同班 现在关系好像也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 居然在那种地方…对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不害臊的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我和杏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里已经传遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天和杏接吻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个应该说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近本来就觉得你哪儿不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙地会高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 和我交往的是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你和藤林椋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么意外吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们根本是不同类人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏的话还能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我随便下定论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…这流言也会传到藤林那儿吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学校的话 不想听也会听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我走一趟 不会花你很长时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么都没干啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 杏！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 我说的事有那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 事前根本没有任何征兆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗 因为太过接近所以发觉不了的那种？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 差不多是那样的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我给你个简单明了的证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说错了 我抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏你喜欢的是冈崎吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你瞎说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 为了消除关于自己和你的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算用和我交往来解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只是流言的话她就不会做这种事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别把阳平说的那些话当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你和椋那么要好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也不由得想找个男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就找阳平当对象试试了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就以这么随随便便的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来交男朋友的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关你的事才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要把椋放在心上就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女朋友担心的人最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想试试叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 杏她对我都是直呼本名…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都已经是现在这种关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 也请叫我椋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 椋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋…朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去春原那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期天 没人会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹 给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和椋去约会了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是全湿透了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要考虑椋的事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是椋的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不放下我的事 是不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再搭理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很笨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我好的话 我会误会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕对你表白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你表白以后 万一被拒绝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能连朋友的关系也不能维持了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和你交往的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会让椋伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 还不如选择放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为这样大家都不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我却后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很傻对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是自己下的决定却…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤林杏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是椋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是个麻烦的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和双胞胎姐妹的这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你会怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在你这种情况下嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个我都收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把你揍到残废吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 开玩笑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话确实不好办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是打算对姐妹俩都保持距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是最差劲的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想着怎么能洁身自保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你如何选择 都会伤害到其中一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越晚做出抉择 留下的伤口就会越深的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们三人中的每一个来说都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再多说一句吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这烦恼也太奢侈了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃饭吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么话要和我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们两个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫画里边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后的教室里两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会做像接吻之类的事情吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不用名字叫我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输给姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的眼光一直在注视着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道 我却还是去找姐姐商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和朋也君做朋友的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐虽然先是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但马上就对我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「包在我身上」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她会那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道自己这样做很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 就算这样我也想待在朋也君的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就不能成为姐姐的替代吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会更加像姐姐那样活泼主动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把头发留长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会去学做一手好菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为朋也君理想中的女性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事情不是我希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望能留在朋也君的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么由铃木来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你交往的这段日子 真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人所需要是多么美好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以为我们可以顺利地继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了最差劲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和你在一起 眼里却看着别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管发觉了这件事 却还瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用了你的温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 你的头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被教训了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋她对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不准逃避！」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本希望一直这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边伤害着椋一边和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做这种肮脏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她却说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那是不可能的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「已经太迟了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你如果真心喜欢朋也 就不能再逃避了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们俩无论如何都会受伤的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因为我们喜欢上了同一个人啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定在流着眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 真是太迟了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉彼此的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有正视对方也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 彼此伤害的事就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是她 是我 还是朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直…都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你道歉 然后原谅你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得我们的一切就会变成虚假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能好好珍惜那一段时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 是不是说好了去哪玩来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 那个取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋说一起去购物 已经很久没约过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.37,0:22:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没办法咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 选择了我真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会觉得 还是和椋在一块比较轻松？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 我可要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话会让我更安心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得那样太拐弯抹角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用更简单明了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
